==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solid-drawn
<hw>Sol"id-drawn`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Drawn out from a heated solid
bar, as by a process of spiral rolling which first hollows the bar and
then expands the cavity by forcing the bar over a pointed mandrel fixed
in front of the rolls; -- said of a weldless tube.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solidifiable</ent>⟦br⟧
